metadata.description:
"not a dj", young thrift gawd is a vibe whisperer est. lit nft gang discord days. They mixed music from my new album "EVOLUTION" into "3VOLUTION" a mini generative project perfect for the dance floor and the party in your headphones. Three celebratory volumes, three vibes! Collect this sound and/or all three and swap mixes with other collectors across web3. 

Top 8 collectors receive a link to the EVOLUTION album, all collectors welcome to join the "EVOLUTION to 3VOLUTION" a hybrid chat, live-stream, and irl meetup community in and out of web3.
